Outdated Software/Operating System
Customer Recommendation Action: 

Update <operating system/agent/software> on <host(s)> to the latest version or apply relevant patches and updates as soon as possible.

Customer Recommendation Reason: 

Outdated software and operating systems can contain known vulnerabilities that may be exploited by attackers to gain unauthorized access or execute malicious code. Keeping software and operating systems up-to-date with the latest patches and updates helps to mitigate these risks and enhances overall security posture.

